' Verified against:
'   Modules/Shared/System/Controllers/HiringRequirementController.cs
'       [Route "api/v1/hiring-requirements"]:22, [Authorize]:23
'       GenerateArtifacts:166-204 (fire-and-forget Task.Run:184)
'       GetArtifacts:206 · GenerateArtifact (single):309 · CancelArtifacts:352
'       progress-stream (SSE):466
'   Modules/Shared/System/Services/HiringRequirementService.cs
'       GenerateArtifactsAsync:564-736  -> path "/api/v1/hiring-requirements/generate/stream":627,
'                                          HMAC headers:635-640, SSE loop:644-718,
'                                          SaveArtifactAsync:711, session Completed:720
'       GenerateArtifactAsync:738-930   -> path "/api/v1/hiring-requirements/generate-artifact/stream":823,
'                                          HMAC headers:831-836, SSE loop:838-908
'       PublishAsync:271-405 (RequirementSnapshot + ArtifactSnapshots)
'   Modules/Shared/System/Services/HmacSignatureService.cs
'   CVerify.AI/app/api/routes/analysis_router.py:317, :354
'   CVerify.AI/app/pipelines/requirement/orchestrator.py
'       generate_artifact_stream:67-76 · generate_all_artifacts_async:78-190
'       _call_claude_with_validation:45-65 (Pydantic self-correction retry, max_retries=2)
